        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She remains quiet for some time, as if reluctant to speak.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 65,
        "ActionId": 66,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Forest Guard A', 3: 'I just received a list of the people who went to... the research institute. Almost all the serious injuries and dead are concentrated there.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 66,
        "ActionId": 67,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Forest Guard A', 3: 'As for the names on the list, none of them are included on the civilian registration form, except for a few familiar names.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 67,
        "ActionId": 68,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Forest Guard A', 3: 'It seems that... Before that, some... people were still buried alive with the secrets of the institute.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 68,
        "ActionId": 69,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She hesitated a little when speaking. She wanted to add something worthy, but decided to force it down.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 69,
        "ActionId": 70,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: '...The death toll is lower than anticipated. It\\'s a miracle...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 70,
        "ActionId": 71,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Forest Guard A', 3: 'Out of all of this destruction, that\\'s where most of the casualties are? Did she intentionally cause all of this commotion to give people time to evacuate?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 71,
        "ActionId": 72,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Diana', 3: 'I can\\'t say I believe it, but I\\'d say so based on the death toll... Or was there some hidden motive?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 72,
        "ActionId": 73,
        "NextActionId": null,
