        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Rosetta looks at the excavated ruins below. The three broken stone pillars stand askew at the bottom of the underground research lab, like a bloodthirsty demon, stretching out its sharp claws from the darkness below.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 96,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Closing her eyes, it seems as if she can still hear those cries of desperation echoing in the recesses of the \"Reception Hall of Peace\".'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 97,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The underground research lab, which had brought nightmares to Amberia and countless other people, has now been turned into ruins in a way she cannot possibly have imagined.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She lifts the collapsed stone slab, exposing the bloodstained ruins below. The mix of overlapping bright and dark reds is a silent testimony of their suffering.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Most of those who fled to the research institute knew what secret atrocities were buried here.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'However, it was because of these secrets that they viewed this secret underground research lab as a safe haven.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The armor plating, execution grounds, and observation rooms built to conduct these experiments gave these people the illusion that they would never be found—much like the secrets kept within these confines.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: '\"Sinners should be executed where they committed their crimes,\" Rosetta has heard. And now, seeing all these people buried in the ruins with countless test subjects, she wonders if they were indeed \"sinners.\"'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 101,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory216.png'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Recovering from her brief introspection, Rosetta turns her attention back to the disaster relief work.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 105,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
